# game/Scenes/Whitney/WhitneyDates/whitneyparkdate.rpy:27
translate spanish whitneyparkstartdate_132b2708:

    # "Whitney and I make our way around the trails, chit-chatting for a while."
    "Whitney y yo recorremos los senderos, charlando un rato."

# game/Scenes/Whitney/WhitneyDates/whitneyparkdate.rpy:35
translate spanish whitneyparkstartdate_236ab045:

    # "Eventually, we reach the bench halfway along the trail."
    "Al final, llegamos al banco que hay a mitad del camino."

# game/Scenes/Whitney/WhitneyDates/whitneyparkdate.rpy:41
translate spanish whitneyparkstartdate_c7d49adf:

    # "I sit on the bench and she sits next to me. We hold hands and watch the sky change colors as the sun sets."
    "Me siento en el banco y ella se sienta a mi lado. Nos cogemos de la mano y vemos cómo el cielo cambia de color mientras se pone el sol."

# game/Scenes/Whitney/WhitneyDates/whitneyparkdate.rpy:45
translate spanish whitneyparkstartdate_1afd758f:

    # "Then I lean over and kiss her and we start making out."
    "Luego me inclino y la beso, y empezamos a besarnos."

# game/Scenes/Whitney/WhitneyDates/whitneyparkdate.rpy:46
translate spanish whitneyparkstartdate_6e33dba8:

    # "She's inexperienced, but she's really into it. She kisses with passion and desire. I can tell she wants more."
    "No tiene experiencia, pero le gusta de verdad. Besa con pasión y deseo. Me doy cuenta de que quiere más."

# game/Scenes/Whitney/WhitneyDates/whitneyparkdate.rpy:47
translate spanish whitneyparkstartdate_af7c35f8:

    # "But we have to head back before it gets too dark."
    "Pero tenemos que volver antes de que oscurezca demasiado."

# game/Scenes/Whitney/WhitneyDates/whitneyparkdate.rpy:50
translate spanish whitneyparkstartdate_6524e8a6:

    # wt "This has been really nice, [pcname]."
    wt "Ha sido muy bonito, [pcname]."

# game/Scenes/Whitney/WhitneyDates/whitneyparkdate.rpy:51
translate spanish whitneyparkstartdate_c024991e:

    # wt "Thank you for taking me out. I really should get out in nature more often."
    wt "Gracias por traerme aquí. Debería salir a la naturaleza más a menudo."

